      "firm_id": "optimistic_8",
      "description": "Get ready to be impressed by this absolute gem! This vehicle is in truly mint condition, looking and driving exactly as if it just left the showroom floor. It has been meticulously cared for and remains in flawless shape, both inside and out. If you're looking for a vehicle that's virtually indistinguishable from new, this is the one for you!",
