    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a reliable daily driver with character? This car is in fair condition and ready for its next chapter! It has been well-maintained over the years and offers a steady, dependable ride that gets you where you need to go. While you'll find some honest signs of wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a functional and budget-friendly option for anyone seeking practical transportation. Come see why this honest, hardworking vehicle is a great value for the price!",
      "price": 22000.0,
